==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Coir
<hw>Coir</hw> <pr>(koir)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Tamil
<ets>kayiru</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A material for cordage,
matting, etc., consisting of the prepared fiber of the outer husk of the
cocoanut.</def> <rj><au>Homans.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Cordage or cables, made of this material.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Coistril</ent>⟦br⟧
